        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Trusting Commercial Communications Networks Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Federal Communications Commission to publish a list of communications equipment or services that pose a national security risk and forbids federal funds from being used to purchase such equipment or services.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
